sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User as Patient / User
    participant UI as Group Sessions UI
    participant Classifier as Classifier Service
    participant ChatMgr as Chat Manager
    participant DB as Rooms & Risks DB

    Note over User, Classifier: Step 1: Matching based on Scores
    User->>UI: View "Recommended Groups"
    UI->>Classifier: Get Top Category (Score > 15)
    Classifier->>DB: Check User Risk Level (Red Flags)
    
    alt High Risk (Score >= 50)
        DB-->>Classifier: High Risk Detected
        Classifier-->>UI: Block Group Access & Suggest Private Therapy
    else Safe to Join
        Classifier-->>UI: Show Rooms (e.g., "Work Stress Support")
        
        Note over User, UI: Step 2: Privacy & Identity Choice (US6)
        User->>UI: Select Room & Choose Identity (Nickname/Avatar)
        
        UI->>ChatMgr: Request to Join (Room_ID, Identity_Type)
        
        Note over ChatMgr, DB: Step 3: Capacity & Security Check (UC3)
        ChatMgr->>DB: Check Room Capacity (Current vs Max)
        
        alt Room is Full
            DB-->>ChatMgr: Capacity Reached
            ChatMgr-->>UI: Show Status: "Session Full - Join Waiting List"
        else Room Available
            ChatMgr->>DB: Register User (Anonymized Data)
            DB-->>ChatMgr: Success & Encryption Key Issued
            ChatMgr-->>UI: Access Granted (Enter Room)
            UI-->>User: Welcome to the Group (Identity Protected)
        end
    end